<div class="howto android menu">
<p>Accessing the Recovery Menu:
 1  Turn off the device
 2  Press the Power key with a metallic clip and, immediately after, press the Scan Key

Recovery Menu (Oreo)
 > Reboot system now
 > Apply update from ADB
 > Apply update from external storage
 > Factory Reset
 > Enterprise Reset
 > OTA Update Options
 > Power off</p>
