<div class="howto android os">
<p> 1  Copy the Firmware.zip file to the Downloads folder of the device
 2  From  the  Settings  menu,  tap  System  >  System  upgrade  >  Localupgrade
 3  Tap the menu icon on the top left corner of the screen and then tap Downloads
 4  Select the update package you want to install and tap on install update</p>

 alternatively, perform an update with the recovery menu
